cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on a method for object segmentation and manipulation using a robot. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper involves generating a 3D map from multiple camera viewpoints and evaluating segmentation accuracy. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for multilabel object mapping using probabilistic techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper involves training a model to recognize and manipulate multiple objects. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves controlling a robot to manipulate objects in an environment with heavy occlusions.
